#!/usr/bin/env python3
"""
zebra — text physics engine CLI

Usage:
    zebra extract <file>                     canonical extraction + graph build
    zebra project <name> [--stem STEM]       build one projection from graph
    zebra project all    [--stem STEM]       build all ten projections
    zebra render  <name> [--stem STEM]       render one output
    zebra render  all    [--stem STEM]       render all outputs
    zebra simulate constraints [--stem STEM] run constraint propagation simulator
    zebra crawl <repo_dir>     [--stem STEM]            crawl repo + build corpus graph
    zebra wiki                 [--stem STEM] [--title T] generate Zebrapedia static site
    zebra search <query>       [--stem STEM] [--mode M]  search the corpus graph
    zebra diff <before> <after>                           diff two graphs
    zebra person               [--stem STEM]             build longitudinal person graph
    zebra serve                [--stem STEM] [--port N]  start dev server with live reload
    zebra scripts              [--stem STEM]             generate task scripts from projections
    zebra recycle  <dir>       [--stem STEM]             feed media transcripts back into pipeline
    zebra agent    <cmd>        [args…]                   local capability-aware scheduler agent

Options:
    --stem STEM     override the stem derived from the input filename
    --model MODEL   Ollama model name (default: granite4)
    --help          show this message

Examples:
    zebra extract essay.txt
    zebra project ambiguity
    zebra project ambiguity --stem essay
    zebra render diffusion
    zebra render all --stem essay
    zebra simulate constraints
    zebra simulate constraints --stem essay

Projection names (short aliases accepted):
    narrative     → narrative_film
    diagram       → diagrammatic_structure
    ambiguity     → ambiguity_diffusion
    rhetoric      → rhetorical_voice
    concepts      → concept_map
    procedural    → procedural_transform
    timeline      → timeline_causality
    characters    → character_state
    sonic         → sonic_mapping
    summary       → structural_summary

Render names (short aliases accepted):
    diagram       → diagrammatic_structure
    diffusion     → ambiguity_diffusion
    concept       → concept_diffusion
    constraints   → constraint_dynamics
    timeline      → timeline_causality
    characters    → character_state
    sonic         → sonic_mapping
    film          → narrative_film
    summary       → structural_summary
"""

